snippet.title: Glen And Friends Cooking
snippet.description:
Glen And  Friends Cooking gives you easy to follow video instructions about food,  cooking, recipes, beer, and cocktails.
This cooking channel is all about Glen's love of food and drink, and his passion for film and production. Each week we will upload new recipes, and videos about food and drink, all shot in 4K+ in our backyard kitchen studio. 


Please help support the channel with our monthly 0.99 cent memberships: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsU15yvILBmnHPeAf4SFVaQ/join

If you are in Toronto, the GTA, or Southern Ontario and you want to collab - get in touch - We're interested in projects

Our mailing address is:
